---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'; 
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | 2 Smokin' Barrels">
    <main class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 2.5rem; background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border-radius: 16px; backdrop-filter: blur(12px);">
        <h1 class="page-title" style="font-family: 'Mr Dafoe', cursive; font-size: 3.5rem; color: var(--accent-pink); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(234, 72, 178, 0.6);">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p style="color: var(--white-med); text-align: center;"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> May 10, 2026</p>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">1. Introduction</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">Welcome to 2 Smokin' Barrels ("we," "our," or "us"). Our application uses the YouTube API Services to provide interactive features during our live streams. By using our services, you are agreeing to be bound by the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/t/terms" style="color: var(--accent-pink); text-decoration: underline;">YouTube Terms of Service</a>. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you interact with our website (2smokinbarrels.com) and our live stream Command Center[cite: 18].</p>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">2. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">When you use the Command Center to interact with our live stream, we require authentication via Google Identity Services. If you choose to sign in, we request the following specific data using the YouTube Data API (<code>youtube.readonly</code> scope). For more information on how Google manages your data, please refer to the <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" style="color: var(--accent-pink); text-decoration: underline;">Google Privacy Policy</a>[cite: 18].</p>
        <ul style="color: var(--white-med); padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
            <li><strong>YouTube Channel ID:</strong> To uniquely identify your account in our stream database[cite: 18].</li>
            <li><strong>YouTube Display Name & Handle:</strong> To display your name on our website's user interface and attribute your commands in our stream chat[cite: 18].</li>
            <li><strong>Profile Picture:</strong> To display your avatar locally on your web browser[cite: 18].</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">We use the information collected solely to facilitate your interaction with the 2 Smokin' Barrels live stream. Specifically[cite: 18]:</p>
        <ul style="color: var(--white-med); padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
            <li>To verify your identity when you trigger a stream command[cite: 18].</li>
            <li>To deduct the appropriate stream points[cite: 18].</li>
            <li>To track your persistent variables (like your Word of the Day stats) within our local Streamer.bot database[cite: 18].</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">4. Data Storage and Retention</h3>
        <ul style="color: var(--white-med); padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
            <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Your profile information is temporarily stored in your browser's local storage to keep you logged in[cite: 18].</li>
            <li><strong>Retention:</strong> User data is retained in our local Streamer.bot database for as long as our interactive stream features are active, or until a user requests deletion[cite: 18].</li>
            <li><strong>No Third-Party Sharing:</strong> We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties. Your data is routed securely through an encrypted Cloudflare Tunnel directly to our private, local streaming PC[cite: 18].</li>
            <li><strong>No Email Tracking:</strong> We do not collect or store your email address, nor do we send promotional emails[cite: 18].</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">5. Your Rights and Data Deletion</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">You can sign out of the Command Center at any time. You may also revoke our application's access to your YouTube account at any time via your <a href="https://myaccount.google.com/permissions" style="color: var(--accent-pink); text-decoration: underline;">Google Account Security settings</a>. To request manual deletion of your data from our local database, please contact us[cite: 18].</p>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">6. Contact Us</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to request the deletion of your data, please contact us via our <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--accent-pink); text-decoration: underline;">Contact Form</a>[cite: 18].</p>
            
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">7. Changes to This Policy</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated Effective Date[cite: 18].</p>
    </main>
</Layout>